Sincro: wyxchari

7
00:00:33,561 --> 00:00:36,528
DOCTOR: It's a game, Jamie! They're playing a game!
这是个游戏, Jamie, 他们在跟我玩游戏！

8
00:00:37,278 --> 00:00:41,251
DOCTOR: A rather amusing little game, don't you think so Jamie.
一个很有意思的小游戏，你不觉得吗 Jamie？

9
00:00:42,166 --> 00:00:47,012
DOCTOR: We've done it! Maxtible, they've got the "Human Factor". We've done it!
我们搞定了, Maxtible, 他们得到了“人类特质”, 我们搞定了！

10
00:00:47,166 --> 00:00:51,012
DOCTOR: What are they doing now? Look, they're all joining in. They're playing train!
他们在干什么？看, 他们都连起来了, 他们在玩火车！

11
00:00:53,104 --> 00:00:59,439
DALEK: Train, train, train, train.
火车, 火车, 火车, 火车

12
00:00:59,999 --> 00:01:05,626
DOCTOR: Oh... oh, now what is it? Oh, we're on the roundabout. They're playing roundabout.
噢。。噢, 现在玩什么？哦, 我们被包围了, 他们在玩转圈圈

13
00:01:05,999 --> 00:01:11,626
DOCTOR: Oh, I'm getting dizzy. Oh dear. Oh, oh, ho, ho, oh. I'm dizzy! Oh, ho, ho. I'm dizzy.
噢, 我要晕了。哦, 天啦, 哦, 哦, 哦, 我晕了！哦, 我晕了

14
00:01:12,169 --> 00:01:18,162
DALEK: Diz-yy, diz-yy, dizzy Doctor.
晕-了, 晕-了, 晕-了-博士

15
00:01:18,497 --> 00:01:21,347
DOCTOR: Maxtible, do you hear that? They've got a sense of humour!
Maxtible, 你听到了吗？他们有了幽默感！

16
00:01:21,639 --> 00:01:23,788
MAXTIBLE: I'm glad you are so easily amused.
我很高兴你是如此容易被逗乐

17
00:01:24,233 --> 00:01:27,893
MAXTIBLE: Well, I congratulate you, Doctor. They are almost human.
很好, 恭喜你, 博士。他们很人类

18
00:01:28,112 --> 00:01:28,902
DOCTOR: They are!
的确是！

19
00:01:29,116 --> 00:01:31,902
MAXTIBLE: And I will now leave you to your little game.
我就不耽误你玩你的小游戏了

20
00:01:32,420 --> 00:01:33,421
DOCTOR: Oh, thank you.
哦, 谢谢你

21
00:01:33,981 --> 00:01:36,286
JAMIE: Well, how old are they now, Doctor - mentally?
那, 他们有多大年龄, 博士 —— 从思维上说？

22
00:01:36,513 --> 00:01:41,249
DOCTOR: Oh, they're just young children, but they'll grow up very fast - within a matter of hours.
噢, 他们还只是小孩子, 不过他们会长得很快 —— 只要几个小时

23
00:01:41,513 --> 00:01:46,949
DOCTOR: Now, uh... come here all of you. Come along, gather round.
Come here. Now then, come along, come along.
现在, 你们都过来, 到这里来, 靠拢, 到这里来。来吧, 过来

24
00:01:47,577 --> 00:01:50,478
DALEK: Who is this?
这是谁？

25
00:01:51,364 --> 00:01:54,442
DOCTOR: Oh, this is Jamie. He's a friend.
哦, 这是 Jamie, 他是个朋友

26
00:01:55,083 --> 00:02:00,515
DALEK: Friend. Hello, friend.
朋友。你好, 朋友

27
00:02:00,728 --> 00:02:02,295
DOCTOR: Well, say hello Jamie.
很好, 说你好, Jamie

28
00:02:02,510 --> 00:02:03,329
JAMIE: Hello.
你好

29
00:02:03,539 --> 00:02:09,909
DOCTOR: You know what a friend is, don't you? It's somebody who
...who likes you - who wants to help you and share with you.
你知道什么是朋友, 对不？就是喜欢你的人 - 愿意帮助你, 跟你一起分享的人

30
00:02:10,305 --> 00:02:11,347
DOCTOR: There we are.
好啦, 都到了

31
00:02:11,783 --> 00:02:13,465
DALEK: What have you done?
你做了什么?

32
00:02:13,682 --> 00:02:21,494
DOCTOR: I have given you all names. Alpha, Beta and Omega.
我给你们都取了名字：阿尔法、贝塔、欧米伽

33
00:02:21,792 --> 00:02:33,603
DALEK: Alpha, Beta, Omega. Alpha, Beta, Omega. Alpha, Beta, Omega.
阿尔法、贝塔、欧米伽, 阿尔法、贝塔、欧米伽, 阿尔法、贝塔、欧米伽

34
00:02:33,844 --> 00:02:39,960
DOCTOR: Yes, yes, yes. now... now, this is Jamie and I am Doctor. We are friends.
是的, 是的, 是的。现在。。现在, 这位是 Jamie, 我是博士, 我们是朋友

35
00:02:40,498 --> 00:02:51,916
DALEK: Friends, friends, Jamie, Doctor, friends, friends.
朋友, 朋友, Jamie, 博士, 朋友, 朋友。

36
00:02:52,498 --> 00:02:59,916
DALEK: We must go now. We are called.
我们得走了, 被召唤了

37
00:03:00,155 --> 00:03:06,092
DOCTOR: Go? Go where? What do you mean, "go"?
走？去哪儿？你们什么意思, “走”？

38
00:03:06,489 --> 00:03:11,640
DALEK: All Daleks are ordered to return to Skaro.
所有 Daleks 都被命令返回 Skaro

39
00:03:12,391 --> 00:03:15,072
DOCTOR: Return to Skaro? But, that's the Dalek planet.
返回 Skaro? 但是, 那是 Dalek 的星球

40
00:03:15,539 --> 00:03:17,072
DALEK: Friend.
朋友

41
00:03:18,949 --> 00:03:23,235
JAMIE: But if the Daleks are returning to Skaro, where's Victoria?
如果 Daleks 全都要返回 Skaro, 那 Victoria 呢？

42
00:03:23,658 --> 00:03:27,223
DOCTOR: Victoria! We left her in the secret passage. Come on - follow me!
Victoria! 我们把她忘在秘密通道了, 快, 跟我来！

43
00:03:32,529 --> 00:03:36,808
MAXTIBLE: I assure you, my dear Waterfield, Victoria is perfectly safe.
我向你保证, 我亲爱的 Waterfield, Victoria 现在非常的安全

44
00:03:37,070 --> 00:03:38,417
WATERFIELD: But where is she?
但她在哪儿？

45
00:03:38,628 --> 00:03:40,138
MAXTIBLE: The Daleks have released her.
Dalek 已经放了她

46
00:03:40,674 --> 00:03:41,741
WATERFIELD: Released?
放了？

47
00:03:41,954 --> 00:03:43,340
MAXTIBLE: Yes, yes, yes, yes, yes.
是的, 是的, 是的

48
00:03:43,510 --> 00:03:44,779
WATERFIELD: Well, then, where is she?
那, 她在哪儿？

49
00:03:44,943 --> 00:03:49,011
MAXTIBLE: She's probably lying down. Ruth will be taking care of her. You may be sure of that.
她很可能已经睡觉了, Ruth 在照顾她, 你可以放心

50
00:03:49,156 --> 00:03:54,189
WATERFIELD: Not Ruth, no. I saw her and Mollie helping
Arthur Terrall into a dog-cart not half an hour since.
不会是 Ruth, 不。我看见她和 Mollie 扶着 Arthur Terrall 进了一辆马车, 不到半个小时前

51
00:03:54,418 --> 00:03:55,714
MAXTIBLE: Ruth and Terrall?
Ruth 和 Terrall?

52
00:03:55,913 --> 00:03:59,845
WATERFIELD: Yes. Surely you knew they were leaving?
是, 当然你知道他们离开吧？

53
00:04:00,023 --> 00:04:03,510
MAXTIBLE: Oh, yes, yes, indeed, yes. It, it slipped my memory.
噢, 是的, 是的, 的确是。我都忘了。

54
00:04:04,023 --> 00:04:09,510
MAXTIBLE: Umm... As you see, I'm going for a little trip myself.
I... No doubt, I shall join them.
如你所见, 我也要有一段小旅程了。无疑地, 我会跟他们会合

55
00:04:10,023 --> 00:04:13,510
MAXTIBLE: Well, possibly she's, ah... taking a stroll in the garden.
Go along and see. Go along and see.
。那。。她可能正在花园散步呢。去看看吧, 去看看

56
00:04:13,752 --> 00:04:14,443
WATERFIELD: Yes
好吧

57
00:04:14,737 --> 00:04:19,736
MAXTIBLE: Well, go along man! Go along and see. Find your Victoria.
嗯, 去吧, 去看看, 找到你的 Victoria

58
00:04:19,980 --> 00:04:23,079
<i>(Maxtible gets his traveling bag from a cupboard.)</i>
<i>（Maxtible 从橱柜中拿出了他的旅行包）</i>

59
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,079
MAXTIBLE: Stupid, stupid girl.
蠢人, 愚蠢的女孩儿

60
00:04:29,980 --> 00:04:34,579
<i>(Then he moves to a grey box on the floor and starts to examine it.)</i>
<i>（然后他走近地板上的一个灰色盒子, 开始研究）</i>

61
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,728
DALEK: What are you doing?
你在干什么？

62
00:04:54,954 --> 00:04:56,532
MAXTIBLE: Merely, ah... looking.
只不过是。。。看看

63
00:04:56,970 --> 00:04:58,748
DALEK: Do not touch the instrument.
不要碰这些仪器

64
00:04:59,009 --> 00:05:00,618
MAXTIBLE: What is that box for?
这个盒子是做什么的

65
00:05:00,802 --> 00:05:04,295
DALEK: Do not question. You have your orders.
不要提问, 你要遵循你的命令

66
00:05:04,471 --> 00:05:10,115
MAXTIBLE: Oh, yes, yes, yes, yes. To... To bring the Doctor
and his companion to you here for our little trip.
噢, 是, 是, 是, 是。要把博士和他的同伴给你们带来, 一起进行我们的小旅程

67
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,101
DALEK: Yes
是的

68
00:05:11,311 --> 00:05:14,264
MAXTIBLE: And then... The secret - you will give it to me?
然后。。那个秘密 - 你们会给我的吧？

69
00:05:14,713 --> 00:05:15,549
DALEK: Yes.
是的

70
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:17,748
MAXTIBLE: The formula - the transmutation formula.
秘方 - 转换秘方

71
00:05:17,944 --> 00:05:24,339
DALEK: Yes. Obey your order. Do not delay.
是的。服从你的命令, 不要延误

72
00:05:24,544 --> 00:05:28,639
<i>(The Dalek returns to the cabinet.)</i>
<i>（Dalek 返回到柜子里去了）</i>

73
00:05:29,144 --> 00:05:33,639
<i>(Maxtible continues examing the machine.)</i>
<i>（Maxtible 继续研究那个机器）</i>

74
00:05:49,996 --> 00:06:00,997
MAXTIBLE: Doctor, Doctor! Doctor!
博士, 博士, 博士！

75
00:06:01,273 --> 00:06:04,788
MAXTIBLE: Oh, Waterfield, how I'm delighted you've come back.
噢, Waterfield, 我很高兴你回来了

76
00:06:04,973 --> 00:06:10,788
MAXTIBLE: Now will you please go and find the Doctor and his companion
Jamie and bring them here to me? It is a matter of some urgency.
你能不能去找到博士和他的同伴 Jamie, 把他们带来见我？这里有点急事

77
00:06:11,319 --> 00:06:12,287
WATERFIELD: Maxtible?

78
00:06:12,514 --> 00:06:13,436
MAXTIBLE: Oh, what is it?
哦, 什么事？

79
00:06:13,744 --> 00:06:15,748
WATERFIELD: What have you "arranged" with the Daleks?
你跟 Daleks 在策划什么事情？

80
00:06:16,019 --> 00:06:17,283
MAXTIBLE: The Daleks; nothing.
Daleks？ 没有啊

81
00:06:17,457 --> 00:06:19,301
WATERFIELD: What formula did they promise you?
他们承诺给你什么秘方？

82
00:06:19,496 --> 00:06:20,934
MAXTIBLE: No formula whatever.
没什么秘方

83
00:06:21,210 --> 00:06:26,231
WATERFIELD: What are you doing? You've sold yourself to them, haven't you?
你做些什么？你把自己卖给了他们, 是不是？

84
00:06:26,410 --> 00:06:27,595
MAXTIBLE: You fool!
傻人

85
00:06:27,813 --> 00:06:33,473
WATERFIELD: Yes, I'm a fool - a fool not to have realised before
that it was you who brought this misery down on us.
是的, 我很傻, 傻到一直都没有意识到, 带给我们这些悲剧的, 正是你

86
00:06:33,735 --> 00:06:42,353
MAXTIBLE: You, you never did understand anything, did you?
Well, metal into gold. That's what the Daleks are going to give me.
你, 你从来就什么都不明白, 是吧。好吧, 金属变成金子, 那就是 Dalek 要给我的秘方

87
00:06:42,735 --> 00:06:49,353
MAXTIBLE: Now do you begin to understand? The secret of the transmutation of metal into gold.
现在你明白了吗？将金属变成金子的秘密

88
00:06:49,584 --> 00:06:52,734
WATERFIELD: Do you imagine I care about that?! Where is Victoria?
你以为我在乎那个吗？ Victoria 在哪儿！

89
00:06:52,932 --> 00:06:54,094
MAXTIBLE: I've not the remotest idea.
我完全不知道

90
00:06:54,308 --> 00:06:56,210
WATERFIELD: Yes, you have, and you're going to tell me!
你知道, 而且你会告诉我！

91
00:06:56,387 --> 00:07:07,692
MAXTIBLE: Get your hands off my throat. Let go of me! Murder!
Murder! Murder! Murder! Murder! Murder! Murder! Murder! Oh.
别用手掐我的喉咙, 放开我！谋杀啊, 谋杀, 谋杀。。。。。噢 

92
00:07:12,539 --> 00:07:14,191
MAXTIBLE: Oh, what are you doing?
噢, 你在干什么？

93
00:07:14,420 --> 00:07:15,555
DALEK: Where is the Doctor?
博士在哪儿？

94
00:07:15,788 --> 00:07:17,130
MAXTIBLE: Well, I had no time to bring him.
呃——我还没时间把他带来

95
00:07:17,316 --> 00:07:19,253
DALEK: Hurry. That is an order.
快去, 这是命令

96
00:07:19,446 --> 00:07:21,447
MAXTIBLE: What is that box for? Will you tell me?
这个箱子是做什么的, 你能告诉我妈

97
00:07:21,695 --> 00:07:24,056
DALEK: We are destroying this area.
我们要摧毁这片区域

98
00:07:24,361 --> 00:07:29,061
MAXTIBLE: But you can't do that. Turn it off! You cannot destroy my house!
你不能这么做, 关掉它！你不能摧毁我的房子！

99
00:07:29,259 --> 00:07:32,041
DALEK: Bring the Doctor. Obey! Immediately!
把博士带来, 服从！马上！

100
00:07:32,250 --> 00:07:38,864
MAXTIBLE: But, uh... the secret. If you destroy my laboratory,
the secret is useless! You promised me.
但是。。秘密呢？如果你毁了我的实验室, 秘密就没有用了！你许诺过我的

101
00:07:39,050 --> 00:07:48,864
MAXTIBLE: They must be out of their minds! Destroy my laboratory?
The very idea... Well, well.
他们一定是疯了！要毁了我的实验室？这个想法。。。好吧, 好吧

102
00:07:49,250 --> 00:08:08,864
MAXTIBLE: But, oh, goodness gracious me, only two minutes. Doctor, Doctor, Doctor...
只是, 噢, 乖乖, 只有两分钟了。博士, 博士, 博士。。。

103
00:08:09,650 --> 00:08:14,864
<i>(Maxtible enters the Dalek cabinet.)</i>
<i>（Maxtible 也进了 Dalek 那个柜子）</i>

104
00:08:26,278 --> 00:08:31,135
DALEK: All Daleks return to Skaro.
所有 Daleks 返回 Skaro

105
00:08:31,950 --> 00:08:36,864
<i>(The Daleks begin to move into the cabinet.)</i>
<i>（所有 Dalek 陆续进入柜子）</i>

106
00:08:37,397 --> 00:08:40,850
DALEK: All Daleks return to Skaro.
所有 Daleks 返回 Skaro

107
00:08:41,107 --> 00:08:41,583
DALEK: And the prisoners?
囚犯怎么安排？

108
00:08:41,777 --> 00:08:44,954
DALEK: They are already in transit.
他们已经在路上了

109
00:08:45,234 --> 00:08:51,077
WATERFIELD: Doc... Dalek... Doctor.
博。。Dalek。。博士。。

110
00:08:51,195 --> 00:08:53,246
DOCTOR: Waterfield, what's happened to you?
Waterfield, 你怎么了？

111
00:08:53,384 --> 00:09:00,308
WATERFIELD: Doc... Doctor, Daleks are going to destroy... house. Can't turn it off.
博。。博士, Daleks 要毁灭。。房子, 我关不掉

112
00:09:00,423 --> 00:09:02,152
DOCTOR: But, this is a time switch.
是, 这是个计时器

113
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:03,678
JAMIE: Well, if you can't turn it off, surely...
不过, 如果你不能关掉他, 还是可以。。。

114
00:09:03,936 --> 00:09:09,287
DOCTOR: No, wait a minute. Eighty-nine, eighty-eight, eighty-seven.
Just about a minute, that's all we've got.
不, 等等, 89, 88, 87.。。只有一分多钟了, 我们只有这么多

115
00:09:09,455 --> 00:09:11,313
JAMIE: Well, toss it out the window then.
那, 把它扔到窗户外面去啊

116
00:09:11,382 --> 00:09:15,644
DOCTOR: This isn't a firework. We'd have to toss this half a mile.
We'll have to follow the Daleks to Skaro.
这可不是烟花, 我们得把它扔到半英里以外才行。我们只能跟着 Daleks 到 Skaro 去了

117
00:09:15,882 --> 00:09:18,844
DOCTOR: Jamie, open the doors. Come along.
Jamie, 把门打开, 快来

118
00:09:19,875 --> 00:09:21,261
JAMIE: Doctor, they're locked. They won't budge!
博士, 门被锁住了, 推不动

119
00:09:21,430 --> 00:09:24,748
MAXTIBLE: Cupboard in the alcove. The time machine.
壁橱里面的柜子, 那个时间机器

120
00:09:24,953 --> 00:09:32,915
DOCTOR: Time machine! Jamie, give me a hand. Come on.
Quickly. Quickly. Here, now... Here, take this.
时间机器！Jamie, 给我搭把手, 来, 快, 快点, 现在。。。这里, 抓住这个

121
00:09:28,950 --> 00:09:33,864
<i>(The Doctor and Jamie drag the Dalek's time machine from the alcove.)</i>
<i>（博士和 Jamie 竭力把 Dalek 的时间机器往柜子里面拖）</i>

122
00:09:34,587 --> 00:09:36,117
DOCTOR: Now the other one. Steady.
现在, 另外一头, 稳住

123
00:09:42,180 --> 00:09:43,297
JAMIE: Right. Now, where's Victoria?
好。对了, Victoria 在哪儿

124
00:09:43,484 --> 00:09:45,193
DOCTOR: Quick Jamie, the time switch!
快 Jamie, 那个时间开关

125
00:09:48,783 --> 00:09:53,682
JAMIE: Twenty-eight, Doctor. Hey, Doctor, Kemel must have dropped this.
28秒, 博士。嘿, 这肯定是 Kemel 掉下来的

126
00:09:53,882 --> 00:09:54,837
DOCTOR: Jamie!

127
00:09:56,697 --> 00:10:00,180
<i>(The Doctor and Jamie help Waterfield to stand in the machine.)</i>
<i>（博士和 Jamie 帮助 Waterfield 在机器里面站稳）</i>

128
00:09:57,097 --> 00:09:59,480
JAMIE: We'll find Victoria and Kemel too.
我们得找到 Victoria, 还有 Kemel

129
00:10:00,297 --> 00:10:03,180
<i>(Then they get in.)</i>
<i>（然后他们进了Daleks 的时间机器）</i>

130
00:10:27,797 --> 00:10:33,180
<i>(Victoria comes to and sees that Kemel is squeezing
out a cloth from a bowl of water.)</i>
<i>（Victoria 苏醒过来, 看到 Kemel 正在拧一块手绢, 那手绢显然刚从一碗水里捞出来）</i>

131
00:10:37,157 --> 00:10:43,173
VICTORIA: Dear Kemel. Oh, there. Are any of the others here?
亲爱的 Kemel, 噢, 这里还有其他人吗？

132
00:10:43,297 --> 00:10:45,280
<i>(He shakes his head.)</i>
<i>（Kemel 摇摇头）</i>

133
00:10:45,512 --> 00:10:46,768
VICTORIA: The Daleks?
有 Daleks？

134
00:10:46,917 --> 00:10:49,880
<i>(He nods.)</i>
<i>（Kemel 点点头）</i>

135
00:10:53,109 --> 00:10:55,269
DALEK: You will wait here.
你们在这里等着

136
00:10:56,408 --> 00:10:57,929
VICTORIA: Oh, Mr. Maxtible.
哦, Maxtible 先生

137
00:10:58,201 --> 00:10:59,566
MAXTIBLE: Oh, what are you doing here?
啊, 你在这里做什么？

138
00:10:59,934 --> 00:11:02,637
VICTORIA: Don't know. Nor even where here may be.
不知道, 甚至都不知道这里是哪里

139
00:11:00,917 --> 00:11:04,880
<i>(The Dalek leaves.)</i>
<i>（Dalek 离开了）</i>

140
00:11:03,039 --> 00:11:08,283
MAXTIBLE: Oh, we've been transported to the Dalek planet, my dear. To Skaro.
哦, 我们被传送到了 Dalek 母星, 亲爱的, 它叫 Skaro

141
00:11:08,951 --> 00:11:11,026
VICTORIA: I don't understand you.
我听不明白

142
00:11:11,252 --> 00:11:13,377
MAXTIBLE: A little journey through space.
穿越空间的一趟小旅程

143
00:11:13,813 --> 00:11:17,459
VICTORIA: They've taken us somewhere. Is that what you mean?
Away from your house?
他们把我们带到了某个地方, 你是这个意思吗？不在你的房子里了？

144
00:11:17,680 --> 00:11:20,946
MAXTIBLE: Oh, far away. Far, far away.
噢, 离那里很远, 很远

145
00:11:21,260 --> 00:11:23,472
VICTORIA: But why? What do they want?
但是为什么？他们想要什么？

146
00:11:23,687 --> 00:11:27,714
MAXTIBLE: Well, I know why I am here. But why you are here,
I have not the faintest idea.
嗯, 我知道我什么在这里。但你为什么在这里, 我就一点都不清楚了

147
00:11:28,138 --> 00:11:30,725
VICTORIA: You seem to understand them. Ask them.
看来你很了解他们, 那问问他们

148
00:11:30,950 --> 00:11:32,999
MAXTIBLE: Don't be foolish, girl. I shall do no such thing.
别犯傻了, 姑娘。我才不做这种事情

149
00:11:33,195 --> 00:11:34,537
VICTORIA: And where's my father?
还有, 我的父亲在哪儿？

150
00:11:34,726 --> 00:11:36,789
MAXTIBLE: I do not know. I'm not a nursemaid to your father.
我不知道, 我又不是你父亲的保育员

151
00:11:39,775 --> 00:11:41,896
DALEK: Follow me.
跟我来

152
00:11:42,300 --> 00:11:46,512
MAXTIBLE: Of course, I shall do my best for you.
The matter is really entirely out of my hands.
当然, 我会尽量帮你的。现在的情况真的完全不在我的掌握之中了

153
00:11:50,173 --> 00:11:54,294
VICTORIA: It's no good. He won't help us.
这没用的, 他不会帮我们

154
00:11:50,173 --> 00:11:52,294
VICTORIA: Think so? Wish I did.
你这么想？期望我也是

155
00:11:55,173 --> 00:12:03,294
VICTORIA: Don't worry Kemel, I shall protect you.
别担心 Kemel, 我会保护你

156
00:12:05,173 --> 00:12:10,294
VICTORIA: I shall see they do you no harm.
我不会让他们伤害你的

157
00:12:12,173 --> 00:12:21,294
VICTORIA: Yes, I suppose it was a bit silly.
是的, 我觉得这有一点傻

158
00:12:33,066 --> 00:12:38,403
VICTORIA: Oh well. Maybe between us we can fight them.
We must face it out together.
噢, 好吧, 也许我们两个可以跟他们斗。我们必须一起面对

159
00:12:42,530 --> 00:12:45,382
WATERFIELD: And that is the Dalek city?
这就是 Dalek 之城？

160
00:12:45,844 --> 00:12:47,291
DOCTOR: Yes, it is.
是的, 它就是

161
00:12:47,621 --> 00:12:49,987
JAMIE: I've scouted around, but I can't see any water.
我四周探查过了, 没看见有水

162
00:12:50,274 --> 00:12:52,445
WATERFIELD: Oh, please don't bother. I feel much better.
哦, 别麻烦了, 我感觉好多了

163
00:12:52,709 --> 00:12:53,550
DOCTOR: Are you sure?
你确定吗？

164
00:12:53,797 --> 00:12:54,387
WATERFIELD: Yes.
是的

165
00:12:54,592 --> 00:12:56,310
DOCTOR: Come along then. We must get along.
过来吧, 我们必须一起

166
00:12:56,519 --> 00:12:57,597
JAMIE: You mean just walk into the city?
你是说用脚走进这城市？

167
00:12:57,771 --> 00:13:04,078
DOCTOR: Oh, no Jamie. The city is all around us. At least,
um, it's beneath us. Come along.
哦, 不, Jamie, 这座城市就在我们周围。至少, 它在我们下面, 过来吧

168
00:13:07,817 --> 00:13:12,580
<i>(The Doctor moves a boulder, revealing a hold in the rock face)</i>
<i>（博士移动了一块大圆石, 石头表面露出了一个洞）</i>

169
00:13:12,934 --> 00:13:14,497
JAMIE: How long have you known that's there?
你什么时候知道这里有个入口？

170
00:13:14,653 --> 00:13:18,723
DOCTOR: Not a sound. I think the Daleks are in for a little surprise.
别出声。我想 Dalek 会得到一个小惊喜

171
00:13:15,834 --> 00:13:18,497
<i>(They enter the cave.)</i>
<i>（他们进入了洞内 )</i>

172
00:13:32,417 --> 00:13:34,027
DALEK: Where is the Doctor?
博士在那里?

173
00:13:34,775 --> 00:13:36,868
MAXTIBLE: I had no time to get him.
我没时间去找他

174
00:13:37,095 --> 00:13:38,236
DALEK: No time?
没有时间？

175
00:13:38,470 --> 00:13:41,390
MAXTIBLE: I was told my house was going to be destroyed. Why?
我被告知我的房子马上就要被炸毁了。为什么？

176
00:13:41,582 --> 00:13:43,506
DALEK: You did not bring the Doctor?!
你没把博士带来？！

177
00:13:43,725 --> 00:13:50,594
MAXTIBLE: Everything I possess is in that house. Everything.
What right had you or anyone to destroy it?
我喜欢的所有东西都在那栋房子里, 所有。你有什么权利把它毁掉？

178
00:13:50,725 --> 00:13:56,594
MAXTIBLE: All these years of labour, all these years of research
- destroyed through this caprice of yours.
这些年所有的辛苦, 所有的研究 —— 都因为你们的反复无常给毁了

179
00:13:56,725 --> 00:14:02,594
MAXTIBLE: My laboratory - the only real thing in the whole of my existence - destroyed.
我的实验室, 我存活于世唯一真实的东西, 被毁掉了

180
00:14:02,725 --> 00:14:08,594
MAXTIBLE: I, Theodore Maxtible, made a bargain with you,
and I demand to know... ah, ah!
我, Theodore Maxtible, 咱们谈好了的, 现在我要求知道。。。啊, 啊！

181
00:14:09,599 --> 00:14:12,910
DALEK: Rights? You have disobeyed a Dalek command.
You must obey the Dalek command.
权利？你违背了 Dalek 的命令。你必须服从 Dalek 的命令

182
00:14:13,265 --> 00:14:16,189
DALEK: Exterminate. Destroy.
终结。毁灭

183
00:14:16,467 --> 00:14:21,153
MAXTIBLE: I swear... I swear... I swear it's not my fault.
I swear it's not my fault. I... No!
我发誓。。我发誓。。我发誓, 不是我的错, 我发誓不是我的错。我。。。不！

184
00:14:24,633 --> 00:14:25,745
DALEK: Move.
走

185
00:14:26,763 --> 00:14:29,379
MAXTIBLE: What's happening? What are you going to do with me?
发生了什么？你们打算拿我怎样样？

186
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:31,725
DALEK: Obey. Move.
服从。走。

187
00:14:54,151 --> 00:14:56,744
DALEK: These humans are still here.
那几个人类还在这里

188
00:14:56,939 --> 00:15:00,117
DALEK: Then other humans are inside the city.
那城市里面还有其他的人类

189
00:15:03,834 --> 00:15:06,297
<i>(The Daleks leaves.)</i>
<i>（Daleks 都离开了)</i>

190
00:15:06,615 --> 00:15:09,113
VICTORIA: "Other humans inside the city", Kemel! Listen!
”城市里面有其他的人类“, Kemel, 听！

191
00:15:09,608 --> 00:15:19,555
DALEK: Emergency. Emergency. Human beings detected in city! Emergency! Emergency!
紧急情况, 紧急情况。探测到有人类在城市里。紧急情况, 紧急情况！

192
00:15:19,756 --> 00:15:23,216
VICTORIA: Maybe it's Jamie and the Doctor. Oh, Kemel, there's a chance. A chance.
有可能是 Jamie 和博士。哦, Kemel, 有机会了, 有机会

193
00:15:23,432 --> 00:15:33,706
DALEK: Intruders detected. Emergency! Emergency! Human beings detected in city.
检测到闯入者。紧急情况, 紧急情况！检测到有人类在城市里

194
00:15:34,432 --> 00:15:44,606
DALEK: Emergency! Emergency! Intruders detected. All Daleks to observation stations.
紧急情况, 紧急情况！检测到闯入者。所有 Dalek 进入观察岗

195
00:15:44,932 --> 00:15:51,706
DALEK: Repeat. All Daleks to observation stations. Emergency!
重复。所有 Dalek 进入观察岗。紧急情况!

196
00:15:53,834 --> 00:15:58,497
<i>(They are moving along a metal pathway, with a rock wall one side
and a large drop the other.)</i>
<i>（他们沿着一条金属做成的小路前进, 小路一边是石头墙, 另一边是深渊)</i>

197
00:16:31,197 --> 00:16:40,152
DALEK: Stop! What is that mark?
停下！ 那个标志是什么？

198
00:16:40,509 --> 00:16:42,952
DALEK 2: That is my name.
那是我的名字

199
00:16:43,194 --> 00:16:44,104
DALEK: Name?
名字?

200
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:47,064
DALEK 2: The Doctor gave it to me.
博士给我取的

201
00:16:47,304 --> 00:16:48,394
DALEK: Doctor?
博士

202
00:16:48,578 --> 00:16:52,828
DALEK 2: Yes. He is my friend.
是的, 他是我的朋友

203
00:16:53,069 --> 00:16:54,566
DALEK: Follow me.
跟我来

204
00:16:54,834 --> 00:16:58,497
<i>(The two Daleks move down the corridor.)</i>
<i>（两个 Daleks 沿着走廊走过去)</i>

205
00:17:02,834 --> 00:17:07,497
<i>(A Dalek is herding Victoria and Kemel down the corridor.)</i>
<i>（一个 Daleks 驱赶着 Victoria 和 Kemel 沿着走廊往前走）</i>

206
00:17:20,834 --> 00:17:25,497
<i>(Victoria, Kemel and the Dalek enter the room.)</i>
<i>（Victoria, Kemel 和这个 Dalek 进了房间）</i>

207
00:17:26,990 --> 00:17:28,769
DALEK: Remain here.
呆在这里

208
00:17:30,677 --> 00:17:36,681
MAXTIBLE: What is happening? Do you know? They say there are
other human beings in the city.
什么情况？你们知道吗？他们说城市里有其他人类

209
00:17:43,351 --> 00:17:53,032
MAXTIBLE: Why don't you answer me, you little fool.
No one can help you here. No one but me.
你为什么不回答我, 你个小傻瓜。这里没有人能够帮助你, 除了我没有人

210
00:17:53,277 --> 00:18:00,714
DALEK: Silence. Follow me. You, wait.
安静。随我来。你, 等着

211
00:18:03,955 --> 00:18:05,626
MAXTIBLE: I can't see anything.
我什么也看不见

212
00:18:06,011 --> 00:18:06,904
DALEK: Move.
走

213
00:18:07,213 --> 00:18:08,891
MAXTIBLE: Where are you taking me?
你要带我去哪里？

214
00:18:19,871 --> 00:18:21,854
VICTORIA: Oh, what are they doing to him?
噢, 他们在对他干什么？

215
00:18:25,377 --> 00:18:29,678
DALEK: You follow. You will wait.
你跟上。你等着

216
00:18:31,390 --> 00:18:33,123
VICTORIA: I'll do as you say.
你们说什么我就做什么

217
00:18:33,336 --> 00:18:40,802
DALEK: Move forward, alone.
往前走, 单独

218
00:18:44,041 --> 00:18:45,549
JAMIE: That was a human voice, I tell you.
那是一个人的声音, 我跟你说

219
00:18:45,732 --> 00:18:46,745
DOCTOR: Perhaps it was, Jamie
也许是吧, Jamie

220
00:18:46,916 --> 00:18:48,150
DOCTOR: We must go more quickly.
我们必须再走快点

221
00:18:49,319 --> 00:18:51,487
JAMIE: Victoria. That was Victoria's voice.
Victoria. 那是 Victoria 的声音

222
00:18:51,676 --> 00:18:55,256
DOCTOR: You can't. Where are you running to? Well, you mustn't.
You'll go over the edge!
你不能, 你跑哪儿去？嘿, 你不能！你会掉下去的！

223
00:18:55,828 --> 00:19:00,832
DALEK: Doctor, I am your friend.
博士, 我是你的朋友

224
00:19:01,341 --> 00:19:05,368
JAMIE: One of your experiments, Doctor. For a moment I thought we were done for!
你的一个实验品, 博士。有那么一会儿我都觉得我们完蛋了

225
00:19:05,768 --> 00:19:07,039
DOCTOR: What is your name?
你叫什么名字？

226
00:19:07,304 --> 00:19:08,752
DALEK: Omega.
欧米伽

227
00:19:09,850 --> 00:19:11,179
DOCTOR: Oh, I see.
哦, 我知道了

228
00:19:11,443 --> 00:19:14,210
DALEK: I have come to lead you.
我是来给你带路的

229
00:19:14,810 --> 00:19:16,306
DOCTOR: Thank you.
谢谢你

230
00:19:17,423 --> 00:19:18,822
JAMIE: Oh, careful.
哦, 小心点

231
00:19:20,110 --> 00:19:25,941
DOCTOR: Oh, ah... I'm all right. Oh, thank you. Ah, lead on.
噢, 啊。。我没事。哦,谢谢你。带路吧

232
00:19:20,110 --> 00:19:25,941
<i>(The Docotor examines the Dalek's base.)</i>
<i>（博士检查了这个Dalek的底座）</i>

233
00:19:26,185 --> 00:19:28,030
DALEk: Follow me.
跟我来

234
00:19:28,495 --> 00:19:29,978
DOCTOR: What was that screaming?
那是什么叫声？

235
00:19:30,196 --> 00:19:31,508
DALEK: A prisoner.
一个囚犯

236
00:19:31,694 --> 00:19:32,349
DOCTOR: Where?
在哪里

237
00:19:32,536 --> 00:19:35,962
DALEK: Follow me. I will show you.
跟我来, 我带你看

238
00:19:39,175 --> 00:19:40,679
JAMIE: What are you doing?
你在干什么？

239
00:19:48,669 --> 00:19:52,613
DOCTOR: Think I don't know my own mark? That wasn't the real Omega at all.
你觉得我不知道自己刻的字？那根本不是真正的欧米伽

240
00:19:52,802 --> 00:19:54,932
JAMIE: Up to all sorts of tricks, aren't they?
他们的伎俩还真是很多啊, 是不？

241
00:19:55,102 --> 00:19:57,751
WATERFIELD: Oh, please. We must reach my daughter.
噢, 别聊了, 我们得赶去我女儿那里

242
00:20:03,596 --> 00:20:08,417
MAXTIBLE: I tell you, they forced me. They threatened to kill us all.
我跟你说, 都是他们逼我的。他们威胁要杀死我们全部

243
00:20:08,596 --> 00:20:11,417
MAXTIBLE: First of all, they ordered me to scream
and I was to make you do the same.
首先, 他们命令我喊叫, 你们也一样fixme

244
00:20:11,815 --> 00:20:13,383
VICTORIA: And you had to do as you were told?
那你就不得不按他们说的做？

245
00:20:13,555 --> 00:20:15,252
MAXTIBLE: I tell you, they threatened to kill me.
我跟你说, 他们威胁要杀死我

246
00:20:15,403 --> 00:20:17,802
VICTORIA: You came up behind me in the dark and twisted my arm.
你在黑暗中从我被后冒出来, 扭了我的胳膊

247
00:20:17,971 --> 00:20:19,386
MAXTIBLE: And what else could I do?
那我还能干什么？

248
00:20:19,611 --> 00:20:23,649
VICTORIA: Oh, if only I'd realised. Why do you think they wanted us to scream like that?
我要是早明白就好了。你不想想, 他们为什么要我们像那样惨叫？

249
00:20:23,887 --> 00:20:24,714
MAXTIBLE: I've no idea.
我也不知道

250
00:20:24,892 --> 00:20:26,719
VICTORIA: You know perfectly well. 
你完全知道。

251
00:20:26,892 --> 00:20:30,919
VICTORIA: There are other people in the city.
They wanted to draw them on. Trap them.
还有其他人类在城里，他们想把那些人吸引过来, 抓住他们

252
00:20:31,092 --> 00:20:34,919
Oh, if only I could have thought quickly. Oh, Kemel.
我要是能早点能想到这个就好了, 噢, Kemel

253
00:20:43,110 --> 00:20:47,941
<i>(They climb through a g??? into a corridor in the Dalek city.)</i>
<i>（博士他们爬到了 Dalek 城市的一条走道上）</i>

254
00:20:53,110 --> 00:20:58,541
<i>(The Doctor looks up and down the corridor,
he decides which way to go and starts to move.)</i>
<i>（博士往走道两头看了看, 挑了一头, 继续往前走）</i>

255
00:20:58,910 --> 00:21:03,541
<i>(Jamie and Waterfield follow.)</i>
<i>（Jamie 和 Waterfield 紧随其后）</i>

256
00:21:06,910 --> 00:21:10,541
<i>(A Dalek is watching them.)</i>
<i>（一个 Dalek 正等着他们）</i>

257
00:21:25,232 --> 00:21:28,892
DOCTOR: No, no. I don't like the look of this. Back the way we came.
不，不，我不喜欢这个样子。回到我们来的路上去

258
00:21:29,510 --> 00:21:33,541
<i>(Two Daleks block their exit.)</i>
<i>（两个 Daleks 堵住他们的退路）</i>

259
00:21:31,958 --> 00:21:33,548
DALEK: Follow me.
跟我来

260
00:21:37,010 --> 00:21:41,941
<i>(They follow the black Dalek.)</i>
<i>（他们只能跟着黑色 Dalek 走）</i>

261
00:21:59,708 --> 00:22:01,747
EMPEROR: Doctor!
博士!

262
00:22:04,607 --> 00:22:06,645
Look at the size of that thing.

263
00:22:07,005 --> 00:22:10,865
EMPEROR: So, you are the Doctor?
这么说, 你就是那位博士？

264
00:22:12,075 --> 00:22:16,704
DOCTOR: We meet at last. I wondered if we ever would.

265
00:22:16,965 --> 00:22:19,621
EMPEROR: The experiment is over.
实验已经结束了

266
00:22:20,001 --> 00:22:27,482
DOCTOR: Yes, I have implanted the "Human Factor" in the three
Daleks that you gave me... When I say run, run!
是的, 你给我的三个 Dalek, 我已经给他们植入了“人类特质”。。。当但我说跑的时候, 跑！

267
00:22:27,722 --> 00:22:29,234
EMPEROR: Speak louder.
大声说话

268
00:22:29,450 --> 00:22:36,504
DOCTOR: Promise me, Jamie. I was merely telling my friend
that the day of the Daleks is coming to an end.
答应我, Jamie —— 我只是在告诉我的朋友们, Dalek 的日子到头了

269
00:22:36,784 --> 00:22:38,380
EMPEROR: Explain.
解释

270
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:45,740
DOCTOR: It's very simple. Somewhere in the Dalek race
there are three Daleks with the "Human Factor"
这很简单, 在 Dalek 族群中某处, 现在有三个带有“人类特质”的 Dalek

271
00:22:45,880 --> 00:22:51,740
DOCTOR: Gradually, they will come to question.
They will persuade other Daleks to question.
慢慢地, 他们就会问问题, 他们也会感染其他 Dalek 来问问题

272
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:53,940
DOCTOR: You will have a rebellion on your planet!
你的星球上就会掀起叛乱！

273
00:22:54,170 --> 00:22:54,911
EMPEROR: NO!
不会！

274
00:22:55,154 --> 00:23:00,043
DOCTOR: I say, yes. I've beaten you and I don't care what you do to me now.
我说, 会！我已经打败了你们, 现在我才不在乎你要拿我怎么样了

275
00:23:00,236 --> 00:23:07,874
EMPEROR: Silence. The "Human Factor" showed us what the "Dalek Factor" was.
安静。“人类特质”向我们展示了“DaleK特质“应该是什么

276
00:23:09,649 --> 00:23:10,755
DOCTOR: What?
什么？

277
00:23:11,496 --> 00:23:12,852
DOCTOR: Well, what does that mean?
那么，那又意味着什么？

278
00:23:13,250 --> 00:23:19,082
EMPEROR: Without knowing, you have shown the Daleks what their own strength is.
你在并不知情的状态下, 你向 Dalek 展示了他们自己的力量所在

279
00:23:20,080 --> 00:23:23,337
WATERFIELD: While you were doing one thing, they were really making you do another.
让你做一件事，但实际上是在让你做另外一件事

280
00:23:23,643 --> 00:23:28,197
EMPEROR: The "Human Factor" is useless.
”人类特质”是没有用的

281
00:23:28,919 --> 00:23:31,302
DOCTOR: You still have those three Daleks to contend with.
但你仍然有三个 Dalek 要对付

282
00:23:31,546 --> 00:23:40,942
EMPEROR: They will be impregnated with the "Dalek Factor".
Your discovery, but your work is not over.
他们将会被植入"Dalek特质“, 你的探索和工作还没有完啊

283
00:23:41,900 --> 00:23:43,996
DOCTOR: I won't work for you!
我不会为你工作的！

284
00:23:44,246 --> 00:23:45,405
EMPEROR: You will obey!
你会服从的！

285
00:23:45,767 --> 00:23:46,961
JAMIE: What is the "Dalek Factor"?
“Dalek特质”是什么？

286
00:23:47,406 --> 00:23:53,891
DOCTOR: You want me to guess? It means to obey, to fight,
to destroy, to exterminate. I won't do it.
你想让我猜吗？它意味着服从、战争、毁灭、终结。我不会干的

287
00:23:54,414 --> 00:23:55,391
EMPEROR: Watch!
看着！

288
00:24:02,560 --> 00:24:04,079
JAMIE: The TARDIS, Doctor!
TARDIS, 博士!

289
00:24:04,464 --> 00:24:13,583
EMPEROR: You will take the "Dalek Factor. "
You will spread it to the entire history of Earth!
你要提取出"Dalek特质”, 并将它散布到地球的整个历史中去！

